A '''megamaser''' was a [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] [[maser]] weapon installed on [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] that was used by the [[Chiss Ascendancy/Legends|Chiss Ascendancy]] aboard large capital ships such as the [[Chiss Star Destroyer]].

